{"type":"message","id":"fdf93ede","parentId":"dd9fb741","timestamp":"2026-06-04T04:08:09.539Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job delivery - it's a reminder/urge message from the cron system, addressed to \"faye-pending-urge-汀桑\". The context mentions \"两天没来了\" (haven't been here for two days) and references an earlier quote \"跟你完全不是一种类型呢\" (completely not the same type as you).\n\nThis seems like a scheduled reminder to check in on someone named 汀桑 (Ting Sang), likely a friend or contact on QQ. The cron seems to be a \"pending urge\" - meaning it's checking if someone hasn't been around and sending a nudge.\n\nLooking at the delivery mode: \"announce\" is the default for isolated agentTurn when omitted. So this message should be delivered to the chat channel.\n\nThe cron is set up with agentId and this is running in an isolated session. The message is in Chinese and seems to be speaking to someone named 汀桑 about a past conversation where they said something ambiguous.\n\nI should check the memory and context to understand who 汀桑 is and what this is about before responding.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_6WDjkEo8vMoA61zQSupB3269","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"汀桑 faye pending urge"},"partialArgs":"{\"query\": \"汀桑 faye pending urge\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_lxs62KMpwur72VkZAy2h2589","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"跟你完全不是一种类型"},"partialArgs":"{\"query\": \"跟你完全不是一种类型\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":5933,"output":308,"cacheRead":7808,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":225,"totalTokens":14049,"cost":{"input":0.00083062,"output":0.00008624,"cacheRead":0.000218624,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001135484}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780546085757,"responseId":"eaf3c208-279d-4d0e-8981-6cabb1169e87"}}
